@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(0.38)
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.73 * v1 + 0.71)) + ((v1 + 0.56 / v1 + 0.32) + (v1 + 0.36 / v2 + 0.79)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.62 / tmp + 0.83)) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.90 * v0 + 0.12)))
    data[tid] = v0
